<i>adverb</i>: 잠잠히 [잠잠히], 잠자코 [잠자코], 살금살금 [살금살금], 살그머니 [살그머니], 벙긋벙긋 [벙귿뻥귿], 벙긋 [벙귿], 묵묵히 [뭉무키], 말없이 [마ː럽씨], 고요히 [고요히], 가만히 [가만히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>잠잠히 [잠잠히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. silently; still</dd><br>
<dd>분위기나 활동 등이 시끄럽지 않고 조용히.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of an atmosphere, activity, etc., being quiet, not noisy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. silently; quietly</dd><br>
<dd>말없이 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of being still without saying anything.</dd><br>
<dd>3. calmly; still</dd><br>
<dd>파도나 바람 등이 움직이지 않고 조용히.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of waves, wind, etc., being quiet without moving.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>잠자코 [잠자코]</dt><br>
<dd>silently; without a word; without comment</dd><br>
<dd>아무 말 없이 가만히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly without saying anything.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>살금살금 [살금살금]</dt><br>
<dd>silently; carefully</dd><br>
<dd>남이 모르도록 눈치를 보며 조심스럽게 조용히 자꾸 움직이는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing one moving carefully, quietly, and repeatedly so that no one notices.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>살그머니 [살그머니]</dt><br>
<dd>silently; carefully</dd><br>
<dd>남이 모르도록 조용하고 조심스럽게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly and carefully so that no one notices.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>벙긋벙긋 [벙귿뻥귿]</dt><br>
<dd>silently</dd><br>
<dd>닫혀 있던 입이나 문 등을 자꾸 소리 없이 살짝 열었다 닫았다 하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a closed mouth or door silently opening and closing repeatedly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>벙긋 [벙귿]</dt><br>
<dd>silently</dd><br>
<dd>닫혀 있던 입이나 문 등이 소리 없이 살짝 열리는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing a closed mouth or door silently opening a little.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>묵묵히 [뭉무키]</dt><br>
<dd>silently; quietly</dd><br>
<dd>말없이 조용하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly without saying a word.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>말없이 [마ː럽씨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. silently; in silence</dd><br>
<dd>아무 말도 하지 않고.</dd><br>
<dd>Without saying anything.</dd><br>
<dd>2. without a word</dd><br>
<dd>불평 없이 묵묵하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Silently without any complaints.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고요히 [고요히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. silently</dd><br>
<dd>시끄럽거나 어지럽지 않고 조용하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly, neither noisily nor confusedly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. serenely; calmly</dd><br>
<dd>강이나 바다 등의 물결이 잔잔하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of a river, the sea, etc., flowing with small ripples.</dd><br>
<dd>3. peacefully; serenely</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 상태 등이 조용하고 평화롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a quiet and peaceful mind or in such a state.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가만히 [가만히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. quietly; motionlessly</dd><br>
<dd>움직이지 않거나 말 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without movement or words.</dd><br>
<dd>2. indifferently</dd><br>
<dd>일을 해결하기 위한 어떠한 대책이나 노력 없이.</dd><br>
<dd>Without any action or effort to solve something.</dd><br>
<dd>3. deliberatey; carefully</dd><br>
<dd>마음을 차분하게 하고 주의를 기울여.</dd><br>
<dd>With calm and care.</dd><br>
<dd>4. silently</dd><br>
<dd>남이 모르게 조용히.</dd><br>
<dd>Quietly so that others will not notice.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>